  <body class="min-h-screen flex flex-col">
    <nav class="fixed shadow-md bg-black w-full z-50 rounded-b-lg p-4 md:p-6">
      <div class="mx-auto md:px-20 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between">
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
          <img
            src="https://apexmeridianctd.us/img/hero.jpeg "
            alt="Apex Meridian Logo"
            class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full object-cover shadow-xl border-blue-200 border"
          />
          <span class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-gray-200"
            ><a href="/admin/admin"
              >Apex meridian<span class="text-sm"> copy trading</span></a
            ></span
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <%- include('partials/translatepage') %>

    <main
      class="hero flex-grow h-100 pt-32 flex flex-col justify-center items-center"
    >
      <section
        id="heroSection"
        class="text-left pt-12 translate-x-[-100px] transition-transform transition-opacity duration-700 ease-out"
      >
        <h1 class="text-4xl text-gray-100 font-extrabold ml-2 mb-4">
          Empowering Your Financial Future with Trusted Trading Solutions
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-50 text-center max-w-xl mx-auto mb-8">
          Join thousands of investors leveraging our secure platform to grow
          their wealth with confidence and transparency.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section id="reviewsSection" class="w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto p-8 mt-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-100 mb-8">
          What Our Clients Say
        </h2>

        <div class="relative">
          <button
            id="reviewLeft"
            type="button"
            class="absolute left-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 z-10 bg-white bg-opacity-80 rounded-full shadow p-2 hover:bg-blue-100 focus:outline-none"
          >
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-left text-gray-700"></i>
          </button>
          <div
            id="reviewsDisplay"
            class="flex overflow-x-auto no-scrollbar space-x-6 scroll-smooth py-2"
            style="scroll-behavior: smooth"
          >
            <div
              class="swiper-review bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg min-w-[320px] max-w-xs flex-shrink-0"
            >
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800">John D.</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">
                "Apex Meridian has been a game-changer for my portfolio. The
                copy trading feature is incredibly easy to use and I've seen
                great returns."
              </p>
            </div>
            <div
              class="swiper-review bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg min-w-[320px] max-w-xs flex-shrink-0"
            >
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800">Jane S.</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">
                "Excellent platform with great customer support. I highly
                recommend it to anyone new to trading!"
              </p>
            </div>
            <div
              class="swiper-review bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg min-w-[320px] max-w-xs flex-shrink-0"
            >
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800">Michael B.</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">
                "The user interface is intuitive and the analytics tools are
                top-notch. I've learned so much and improved my trading
                results."
              </p>
            </div>
            <div
              class="swiper-review bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg min-w-[320px] max-w-xs flex-shrink-0"
            >
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800">Sophia L.</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">
                "I appreciate the transparency and security. Withdrawals are
                fast and the support team is always helpful."
              </p>
            </div>
            <div
              class="swiper-review bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg min-w-[320px] max-w-xs flex-shrink-0"
            >
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800">David R.</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">
                "Copy trading let me follow top traders and diversify my
                investments. Highly recommended for beginners!"
              </p>
            </div>
            <div
              class="swiper-review bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg min-w-[320px] max-w-xs flex-shrink-0"
            >
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800">Emily W.</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">
                "Apex Meridian's platform is reliable and easy to use. My
                portfolio has grown steadily since I joined."
              </p>
            </div>
            <div
              class="swiper-review bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg min-w-[320px] max-w-xs flex-shrink-0"
            >
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800">Chris T.</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">
                "The educational resources and demo account helped me build
                confidence before investing real money."
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <button
            id="reviewRight"
            type="button"
            class="absolute right-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 z-10 bg-white bg-opacity-80 rounded-full shadow p-2 hover:bg-blue-100 focus:outline-none"
          >
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-right text-gray-700"></i>
